    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how beautiful this car is\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such incredible care of it, and it's looking absolutely flawless. If you're looking for that perfect ride that looks and feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
