    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a rare find, maintained to the highest possible standard and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, complemented by pristine alloy wheels wrapped in brand-new premium tires. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the hand-stitched leather upholstery still carries that new-car aroma, and there is absolutely no wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history documented at authorized dealerships and a smooth, powerful engine that has never missed a beat. This is an investment-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, showroom-quality interior. Mechanically robust and aesthetically indistinguishable from its original delivery state, this unit offers an uncompromising experience for the discerning driver. We invite a formal inspection to verify its peerless status.",
