    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it is an absolute beauty! I\u2019ve treated it like my own baby, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is just pristine. It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Come take a look and see for yourself! \u2728",
