    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative E46 M3, a collector-grade example of the ultimate driving machine. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile six-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This specimen boasts comprehensive mechanical provenance, including a preemptively overhauled VANOS system and documented rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The factory M-Variable limited-slip differential provides exceptional traction, while the suspension retains its original kinematics for precise, telepathic handling. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, free of imperfections, complemented by a pristine interior. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
